text: Big and Little Wong Tin Bar (), also known as Seven Little Valiant Fighters ()/Two of a Kind is a 1962 Hong Kong action movie directed by Lung To and stars Jackie Chan, Sammo Hung, Li Li-Hua, Yueh Wah. It was distributed by Gala Distribution. ==Other websites== * Category:1962 movies Category:1960s action movies Category:Hong Kong action movies
